<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<chapter id="pi-star">
	<title>Pi-Star Digital Voice Software</title>
	<para>Web UI 地址 http://pi-star/</para>
	<para>用户：pi-star</para>
	<para>密码：raspberry</para>
	<section>
		<title>烧录img镜像文件</title>
		<para>下载镜像文件 http://www.pistar.uk/downloads/</para>
		<para>树莓派 3B+ 目前还没有release，可以使用 beta 版本 http://www.pistar.uk/beta/</para>
		<section>
			<title>Mac</title>
			<para>执行 diskutil list 查看SD卡设备文件名</para>
			<screen>
			<![CDATA[
neo@MacBook-Pro ~/Downloads/Pi-Star_RPiB+_V3 % diskutil list			
			]]>
			</screen>
			<para>我的 SD Card 设备文件是 /dev/disk2，卸载 SD Card</para>
			<screen>
			<![CDATA[
diskutil unmountDisk /dev/disk2			
			]]>
			</screen>
			<para>将镜像文件写入 SD Card</para>
			<screen>
			<![CDATA[
sudo dd bs=4m if=Pi-Star_RPiB+_V3.4.16_10-Aug-2018.img of=/dev/disk2		
			]]>
			</screen>
		</section>

	</section>
	<section>
		<title>释放TF卡空间</title>
		<para>首次使用 dd 烧录 TF 启动后，pi-star 不是使用所有的 TF 空间，需要把卡上不用空间全给树莓派</para>
		<screen>
		<![CDATA[
sudo pistar-expand
sudo reboot
		]]>
		</screen>
	</section>
	<section>
		<title>更新系统</title>
		<screen>
		<![CDATA[
sudo pistar-update && pistar-upgrade -y
		]]>
		</screen>
	</section>
	<section>
		<title>修改权限从 ro 到 rw </title>
		<screen>
		<![CDATA[
rpi-rw		
		]]>
		</screen>
	</section>
	<section id="MMDVMHost">
		<title>MMDVMHost</title>
		<section>
			<title>启动和停止</title>
			<screen>
			<![CDATA[
pi-star@netkiller(ro):pi-star$ systemctl enable mmdvmhost
pi-star@netkiller(ro):pi-star$ systemctl disable mmdvmhost			
			]]>
			</screen>
			<screen>
			<![CDATA[
pi-star@netkiller(ro):pi-star$ systemctl start mmdvmhost
			]]>
			</screen>
			<screen>
			<![CDATA[
pi-star@netkiller(ro):pi-star$ systemctl stop mmdvmhost
			]]>
			</screen>
			<screen>
			<![CDATA[
pi-star@netkiller(ro):pi-star$ systemctl restart mmdvmhost
			]]>
			</screen>
			<screen>
			<![CDATA[
pi-star@netkiller(ro):pi-star$ systemctl status mmdvmhost			
			]]>
			</screen>
		</section>
		
	</section>
</chapter>
